kes、Matt Nicholls 和 Matt Kean 于 2013 年 2 月 12 日通过 Getty Images 为 Metal Hammer 杂志/Future 拍摄肖像。（摄影：Will Ireland/Metal Hammer杂志/未来来自盖蒂图片社/未来来自盖蒂图片社）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-circa-2013-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>宣布为 2013 年 LP <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-bring-me-the-horizon-14264-310613">&#39;Sempiternal&#39;</a>重新发行 10 周年纪念。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/bring-me-the-horizon-malta-weekender-2022-interview-3236681">《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》讲述了这一场景：“当你不是唯一的人时，事情会更好”</a></strong></li></ul><p>为了庆祝乐队第四张录音室专辑问世 10 周年，限量版黑胶唱片和盒式磁带定于 12 月 8 日发行。正如新闻稿中所述，唱片和盒式磁带被描述为“精心制作，以强调音乐和内容”。强调了仍然沉浸在符号学和神秘感中的神秘艺术作品”。<a href="https://bmth.co/SEMP10" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订黑胶唱片。</p><p>在谈到这张专辑时，Bring Me the Horizo​​n 主唱奥利·赛克斯 (Oli Sykes) 表示：“我觉得这张专辑改变了我们乐队的一切，无论是在商业成功方面还是在个人方面。” </p><figure id="attachment_3537911" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3537911" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3537911" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS.jpg" alt="Bring Me The Horizo​​n - 《Semipternal》十周年纪念再版。图片来源：新闻界" width="3000" height="1499" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS-400x200.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS-800x400.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS-696x348.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS-1392x696.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bring-Me-The-Horizon-Semipternal-10th-anniversary-reissue.-Creidt-PRESS-1068x534.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3537911" class="wp-caption-text"> Bring Me The Horizo​​n – 《Sempiternal》十周年纪念再版。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“在这张唱片破裂之前，我一直在与毒瘾作斗争，我和乐队的关系也破裂了，我觉得我能为自己的行为道歉的唯一方法就是努力把一切都倾注到一张唱片中。这张唱片让我们的乐队比以往任何时候都更加亲密，因此它将永远在我心中占有特殊的位置。”</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-bring-me-the-horizon-14264-310613">four-star review of the album</a> , <em>NME</em> shared: “Recent listeners to Nick Grimshaw&#39;s Radio 1 breakfast show have been woken with a jolt following the surprise addition of Bring Me The Horizon to the station&#39;s playlist. The riffs of &#39;Shadow Moses&#39; may be a strange accompaniment to your tea and Weetabix, but it&#39;s all part of the Sheffield metal band&#39;s bid to become a Proper Big Deal in 2013.”</p><p> It continued: “Their fourth album &#39;Sempiternal&#39; is packed full of similar sucker-punch moments, with &#39;The House Of Wolves&#39; and &#39;Antivist&#39; typifying the album&#39;s muscular and impressive anthemics. Ready to break noisily out of the underground, the quintet have made one of the year&#39;s most accomplished metal albums.”</p><p> Back in June, Sykes spoke to <em>NME</em> about the band&#39;s forthcoming album &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-announce-new-album-and-2024-uk-ireland-arena-tour-during-download-set-3453746">Post Human: NeX GEn</a> &#39;, and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-oli-sykes-post-human-nex-gen-politics-addiction-interview-3454494">revealed it was primarily inspired by emo and hardcore</a> .</p><p> “ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a> were the first band that I got into, but when I found <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glassjaw">Glassjaw</a> is when I became obsessed with music and knew I wanted to be a singer, so the album pays homage to that,” Sykes said backstage at Download fest. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bring Me The Horizon - Shadow Moses (Official Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-k9qDxyxS3s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> He continued: “I wouldn&#39;t say it&#39;s a <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/hyper-pop">hyper-pop</a> album, but I&#39;ve definitely been inspired by that world. I admire how obnoxious, trashy and in your face that music feels, which is what I was drawn to when I got into emo, hardcore and screamo.</p><p> “It&#39;s not that we&#39;ve lost that in our music, but as you become a bigger band, things do get more polished. I want to go the opposite way. Let&#39;s be unhinged, let&#39;s stop trying to make all the edges smooth.”</p><p> &#39;Post Human: NeX GEn&#39; will serve as a follow up to their 2020 LP &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-survival-horror-review-2802286">Post Human: Survival Horror</a> &#39;. The album&#39;s release date was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-delay-release-of-post-human-nex-gen-3487550">recently pushed back</a> .</p><p> In other news, Sykes and co. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-announce-2024-australian-tour-with-sleep-token-supporting-3515967">recently announced a 2024 Australian tour with Sleep Token as support</a> slated for next spring.</p><p> This will mark Bring Me The Horizon&#39;s return to Australia since their sets at Good Things Fest in 2022. <a href="https://ticketmaster-au.tm7566.net/c/2862475/431533/7566?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com.au%2Fbring-me-the-horizon-tickets%2Fartist%2F1153598" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for tickets and more information.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-announce-sempiternal-10th-anniversary-vinyl-and-cassette-reissue-3537890">Bring Me The Horizon announce &#39;Sempiternal&#39; 10th anniversary vinyl and cassette reissue</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
